Technical Service Management with Spare Parts Tracking}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0

{\hich\af5\afs22\alang1033\ab0\dbch\afs22\ab0\loch\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b
1. Project Name and Business Description}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0
This project is a Windows desktop application developed for electronic device service businesses. The application helps staff register customers, accept faulty devices, open service requests, track repair operations, manage spare parts usage, and monitor delivery progress.}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0

{\hich\af5\afs22\alang1033\ab0\dbch\afs22\ab0\loch\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b
2. Job Workflow Explanation}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0
1. Reception staff registers a new customer or selects an existing customer.}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0
2. A service request is created for the faulty device.}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0
3. Device information and problem description are recorded.}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0
4. The technician adds service operations and updates status.}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0
5. Spare parts are assigned to the request when needed.}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0
6. Stock quantities are reduced automatically.}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0
7. The manager monitors active jobs, completed jobs, and low-stock parts.}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0

{\hich\af5\afs22\alang1033\ab0\dbch\afs22\ab0\loch\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b
3. Use Case Diagram}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0
Actors: Reception Staff, Technician, Manager.}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0
Main use cases: Register Customer, Create Service Request, Add Service Operation, Assign Spare Part, Update Status, Review Dashboard.}
{\lang1033\par}\pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af7\afs24\alang1081\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang1055\dbch\af9\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang1055\ql\ltrpar{\f5\fs22\lang1033\b0
